  { q: "Are translations required?", a: "Some documents may need English or Arabic translation. We can assist with certified translation services." },
  { q: "Can UAE issued documents be attested for Bahrain?", a: "Yes. We process Indian certificate attestation in Bahrain and UAE documents efficiently through the required procedures." },
  { q: "What if my document is rejected?", a: "Our experts review all documents before submission to prevent rejections. Early review helps avoid repeated submissions and processing delays." },
